se_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10004:\"\n        \n<p>Bonjour  toutes et  tous, dans ce numro je vous explique la diffrence entre co-conception, accessibilit, numrique responsable et qualit web. Autant de termes que lon voit et entend autour de nous sans toujours comprendre ce quils signifient et les actions qui les accompagnent. Nhsitez pas  me dire <a href=\"#reply-title\">en commentaire</a> si cette explication vous aura permis dy voir plus clair. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aprs deux petites informations sur WordPress, je vous parle galement dune catastrophe mondiale vite de justesse il y a seulement quelques jours. Si vous nen avez pas entendu parl, je vous recommande fortement de prendre votre popcorn car cette histoire est incroyable mais vraie. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Je suis Eddy votre <a href=\"https://whodunit.academy/coaching-wordpress-mentorat/\">coach WordPress</a>, bienvenu sur le podcast WOA, votre rendez-vous sur lunivers WordPress</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\">Dans cet pisode :</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list stk-block-icon-list stk-block stk-acab05a\" data-block-id=\"acab05a\"><ul class=\"stk-block-icon-list__ul stk-block-icon-list--column\">\n<li class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list-item stk-block-icon-list-item stk-block stk-0621ff4\" data-block-id=\"0621ff4\"><div class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__content\"><span class=\"stk--svg-wrapper\"><div class=\"stk--inner-svg\"></div></span><span class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__text\">00:00:01 &#8211; Introduction aux thmes du podcast</span></div></li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list-item stk-block-icon-list-item stk-block stk-780cc62\" data-block-id=\"780cc62\"><div class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__content\"><span class=\"stk--svg-wrapper\"><div class=\"stk--inner-svg\"></div></span><span class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__text\">00:00:53 &#8211; Nouveauts sur WordPress 6.5 &#8220;Regina&#8221;</span></div></li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list-item stk-block-icon-list-item stk-block stk-aa11dfa\" data-block-id=\"aa11dfa\"><div class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__content\"><span class=\"stk--svg-wrapper\"><div class=\"stk--inner-svg\"></div></span><span class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__text\">00:02:18 &#8211; Fin du support de PHP 7.0 et 7.1 par WordPress</span></div></li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list-item stk-block-icon-list-item stk-block stk-793433f\" data-block-id=\"793433f\"><div class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__content\"><span class=\"stk--svg-wrapper\"><div class=\"stk--inner-svg\"></div></span><span class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__text\">00:03:11 &#8211; Histoire d&#8217;une catastrophe mondiale vite de justesse</span></div></li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"wp-block-stackable-icon-list-item stk-block-icon-list-item stk-block stk-7a824ed\" data-block-id=\"7a824ed\"><div class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__content\"><span class=\"stk--svg-wrapper\"><div class=\"stk--inner-svg\"></div></span><span class=\"stk-block-icon-list-item__text\">00:07:24 &#8211; co-conception, accessibilit, et qualit web expliqus</span></div></li>\n</ul></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>WordPress 6.5 et ses nouveauts</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dcouvrez ce que Regina apporte dans le monde de WordPress, avec ses amliorations d&#8217;administration et fonctionnalits de personnalisation. Et un point rapide sur la version de scurit 6.5.2. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f6e0.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Fin du support PHP 7.0 &amp; 7.1</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ca y est, plus de support pour les versions PHP 7.0 &amp; 7.1. Quelle version est-il recommand d&#8217;avoir ? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2699.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Rcit d&#8217;une catastrophe vite</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill\" style=\"grid-template-columns:22% auto\" data-block-type=\"core\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\" style=\"background-image:url(https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dallc2b7e-2024-04-12-08-59-29-modify-the-image-of-a-global-web-hacking-scene-due-to-backdoor-xz-to-include-a-warning-sign-prominently-displayed-within-the-control-room-the-warning-617x1080.webp);background-position:50% 50%\"><img width=\"617\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dallc2b7e-2024-04-12-08-59-29-modify-the-image-of-a-global-web-hacking-scene-due-to-backdoor-xz-to-include-a-warning-sign-prominently-displayed-within-the-control-room-the-warning-617x1080.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76597 size-full\" //></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>Accrochez-vous bien pour cette histoire d&#8217;espionnage numrique, o la scurit du web mondial a t menace. Qui est derrire cette tentative audacieuse ? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f575-fe0f-200d-2642-fe0f.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f310.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Clart sur la qualit web et le numrique responsable</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Un plongeon profond dans les termes du numrique responsable. co-conception, accessibilit, inclusivit : comment tout cela s&#8217;assemble pour crer un web de qualit. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f331.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/267f.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" //></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\">Les liens de l&#8217;pisode :</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul data-block-type=\"core\">\n<li data-block-type=\"core\">L&#8217;histoire de la backdoor XZ raconte par Remy : <a href=\"https://piaille.fr/@rusty/112190942173039817\">https://piaille.fr/@rusty/112190942173039817</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\">Fin du support de PHP 7.0 &amp;7.1 : <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2024/04/08/dropping-support-for-php-7-1/\">https://make.wordpress.org/core/2024/04/08/dropping-support-for-php-7-1/</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>N&#8217;oubliez pas, votre feedback est prcieux ; laissez un commentaire ou une note sur votre plateforme d&#8217;coute favorite. Ensemble, illuminons le chemin vers un web plus accessible pour tous.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\">Ecoutez le podcast sur </h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/fr/podcast/woa-wordpress-on-air/id1482779414\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/apple-podcasts-e1571142591535.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66447\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/5rEMqG2cyoKYxpTTUAKSPp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66448\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://www.deezer.com/fr/show/586602\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/deezer-1024x196.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66449\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"http://podplayer.net/?podId=2447675\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/podcast-addict-for-windows-pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66450\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr data-block-type=\"core\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-j-attends-vos-retours-avec-impatience\" data-block-type=\"core\">J&#8217;attends vos retours avec impatience&nbsp;!</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:20% auto\" data-block-type=\"core\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/template-carre-1080x1080.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75791 size-full\" //></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>Je vous invite  couter, partager et surtout  laisser vos commentaires et valuations. Votre feedback est non seulement prcieux pour moi, mais il aide aussi le podcast  toucher un public plus large. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vous souhaitez intervenir ? Envoyez un mail  eddy@whodunit.fr ou rejoignez-moi sur LinkedIn <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/eddy-boels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/eddy-boels/</a> pour en discuter.</p>\n</div></div>\n<p>Larticle <a href=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/ecoconception-accessibilite-sobriete-que-se-cache-t-il-derriere-le-numerique-responsable/\">Ecoconception, accessibilit, sobrit : que se cache-t-il derrire le numrique responsable ?</a> est apparu en premier sur <a href=\"https://www.whodunit.fr\">Agence WordPress Whodunit</a>.</p>\n\n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"\n            \n                                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Eddy Boels\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:6:\"source\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n                    \n                            \n                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"https://www.whodunit.fr/podcasts/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Podcast WordPress on Air!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:8:{s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/wp-youtube-lyte/\";s:7:\"attri